      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MUM'S BOY (6) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 18.66 beating Selena's Chance. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. INFRARED POWER (8) last start finished 4th on March 22 over 312m at this track behind Bing Bing Secret beaten 8 lengths (18.86) in a Grade 4/5. Can feature with the right run. IMPRESS TILLY (2) showed good early speed and led throughout to score her maiden two back then finished third last start and beaten 3.5 lengths at this track over 312m (18.91). Returns to the course where she won her maiden. Expected to feature on best form. TERRITORY TUFF (4) was well backed last start but ran below expectations when fourth (18.60), beaten 4.5 lengths.",
